data.title: Kazakhstan searches for new gas reserves
data.meta_description:
The national company QazaqGaz and the Chevron Corporation, through its subsidiary Chevron Munaigas Inc., signed an agreement on cooperation on exploration work at the Zhalibek site in the Aktobe region near the Zhanazhol and Urikhtau fields.
Negotiations and technical preparations for this project have been carried out over the past year....
data.text:
The national company QazaqGaz and the Chevron Corporation, through its subsidiary Chevron Munaigas Inc., signed an agreement on cooperation on exploration work at the Zhalibek site in the Aktobe region near the Zhanazhol and Urikhtau fields.

Negotiations and technical preparations for this project have been carried out over the past year....
